{"tid":714870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得新聞好應該要audit","createTime":"2018-06-24T03:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T04:56:59.000Z","uid":3425,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"06c6cb8d1640187433ffb0fc8b41b491ed2cd382","tid":714870,"uid":3425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:52:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇隔離po話美國個邊d左膠將個非法移民既女亂咁加一句落去去煽情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n突然忽發其想，覺得其實新聞好需要audit<br />\n唔係每一篇新聞都要事先audit先出街<br />\n而係年度audit咁，對發新聞既機構進行audit<br />\n好似信貸評級咁，俾個rating 個新聞機構<br />\n等讀者自己去信唔信個新聞機構寫既新聞<br />\n而家咁多content farm, d人就咁亂寫一堆野就話係新聞，有左rating就可以等人去分辨個機構信唔信得過<br />\n<br />\n不過技術上應該有好多野要諗，純粹忽發其想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f814adc29620c80e90ce9365519374faa8980c","tid":714870,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪變左自我審查"},{"pid":"3f15eb4336a468d2ac8f5c8d2c681c4b3dbba6e0","tid":714870,"uid":3425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39f814adc29620c80e90ce9365519374faa8980c","tid":714870,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪變左自我審查"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"例如最高評級係不偏不倚<br />\n同埋third party 去audit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\naudit 前定係間野個risk <br />\n如果係high risk 就抽好多單新聞去查係咪報錯<br />\n有冇加入自己既立場咁<br />\n<br />\n目的係令新聞機構可以報道事實，唔係扭曲事實"},{"pid":"04d9442b30f8581d0ef35a0b27c66f77515091a9","tid":714870,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39f814adc29620c80e90ce9365519374faa8980c","tid":714870,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪變左自我審查"},"citedB